chapters.title: The Sixth Feast Which Is the Feast of the Day of Atonement
The Feast of Unleavened Bread Represents the Christian Being Sanctified
The Lord Has Sanctified Him and Made Him Holy the Proof of His Claim to the Blessing Will Be Seen in the Fruit of Meekness
